text: ning aoy khnhom sautr kompir kuor an( aoy mnoussa lok sdab) . dau che neah anaknea haey del ban ttuol kar changaoulobangheanh ku pitabrakd nasa ke nung ttuol ban kar changaoulobangheanh samreab khluon ke phtal . te anaknea haey del ban v nge v ng vinh noh chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha tam pit khnhom kreante chea anak dasatuen promean mneak knongchamnaom anak dasa tuen teanglay bonnaoh
